    "description": "<br>The We Are One Prologue isn't available anymore, if you want to experience a part of the final game before release try the demo on the We Are One page.<br><br>The full game We Are One will contain: A story mode, more content, levels, and mechanics. A level editor will be included in a later update of the full game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6daf8a7a6a9a9529416ef1db499134a0.poster.avif?t=1683312458\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6daf8a7a6a9a9529416ef1db499134a0.webm?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6daf8a7a6a9a9529416ef1db499134a0.mp4?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Love multiplayer but hate other people?</strong><br>We Are One Prologue is a puzzle shooter where you work together with yourself. Every action you perform in a time loop is precisely replicated by a clone of you in the next loop. You have to cleverly plan ahead and cooperate with your clones across time loops to fight back against greasy machines. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6bf90b42df680ff99707cc90f4a13d00.poster.avif?t=1683312458\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6bf90b42df680ff99707cc90f4a13d00.webm?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/6bf90b42df680ff99707cc90f4a13d00.mp4?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/9c7d4f46de1bb9d9fda991df3e49ef13.avif?t=1683312458\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br>You play as a being of nature sent to defend the planet against machines that ruthlessly destroy the environment. Thankfully as a being of nature, you can travel back in time and create clones of yourself. Work together with these past and future versions of yourself to create an army of one and defeat the machines. <br>Experience a variety of levels with new twists and challenges for you and your clones to overcome! If you want something done right do it yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/c702a026737ceee3030c5fcec7b3a60c.poster.avif?t=1683312458\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/c702a026737ceee3030c5fcec7b3a60c.webm?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/c702a026737ceee3030c5fcec7b3a60c.mp4?t=1683312458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855830/extras/e0667a2780869f97875d9284a9237d8a.avif?t=1683312458\" width=600 height=180 /></span><br>We Are One Prologue was designed to be comfortable to play even if you are new to VR or sensitive to motion sickness. There is no artificial locomotion in the game and only teleportation is used. The game was made for both VR beginners and experienced users - It's easy to pick up, but challenging to master.<br>Give it a shot!",
